<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I don't know. The description was really vague. It would be hard to diagnose by today's standards. He must have some kind of mental health/ trauma iss<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I don't know. The description was really vague. It would be hard to diagnose by today's standards. He must have some kind of mental health/ trauma issue to cause that. <br /><br />I wish the author had explained that in more detail. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
