<div id="review_762409824" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/762409824" />
    <a title="Catherine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3496147-catherine"><img alt="Catherine" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389754080p2/3496147.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/762409824?book_show_action=true">Nov 11, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Catherine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Catherine" href="/user/show/3496147-catherine">Catherine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer762409824" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15152081848244886491">Fantastic read. I love historical fiction because it can teach you so much about a particular era. I actually picked up the book based on the beautiful cover and after reading the inside jacket. The story moves along at a good pace and you come to really know the characters. I became a lot more interested in knowing more about the Gilded Age that I was before.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


